Creating zip files

% zip -r Sample.zip Sample.app
  adding: Sample.app/ (stored 0%)
  adding: Sample.app/public/ (stored 0%)
  adding: Sample.app/public/favicon.ico (deflated 37%)
  adding: Sample.app/public/hi.html (deflated 23%)
  adding: Sample.app/Sample (deflated 82%)
  adding: Sample.app/site.nu (deflated 71%)

Increasing process limits
% sysctl kern.maxproc
% sudo sysctl -w kern.maxproc=2000
